To enable easy stub of bls in lodestar, we use babel plugin to gerate rewire code. It appears that it doesn't register those stuff to babel scope tracker.

There is two solutions:

1. remove that plugin and use mockery inside spec tests
   - cons: it intorduces a lot of ugly and unpredicatble code in spec tests as it messes with reqire cache

2. try to register this in babel scope (maybe new version or fork and fix)

